        "keyWord": "on my way ",
        "n": 1,
        "url": "https://isure6.stream.qqmusic.qq.com/C40000344JLF1rEAIE.m4a?guid=cyapi&vkey=FDD236F871431EA34065F28FF8101497BF638969C7D6496FFF9F1E369DD864805F679E2092D2B0D7883E7B4E8B0C8FB99FB7B81C1B192A36__v2b9abf42&uin=2660713565&fromtag=https://cyapi.top",
        "lyric": "[ti:On My Way]\n[ar:Alan Walker/Sabrina Carpenter/Farruko]\n[al:On My Way]\n[by:]\n[offset:0]\n[00:00.00]On My Way (Explicit) - Alan Walker/Sabrina Carpenter/Farruko\n[00:00.04]Lyrics by：Julia Karlsson/Anton Rundberg/Jesper Borgen/Øyvind Sauvik/Sabrina Carpenter/Farruko/Franklin Martinez/Marcos Perez/Gunnar Greve\n[00:00.08]Composed by：Alan Walker/Anton Rundberg/Julia Karlsson/Jesper Borgen/Anders Frøen/Fredrik Borch Olsen/Julia Karlsson/Anton Rundberg/Jesper Borgen/Øyvind Sauvik/Gunnar Greve/Sabrina Carpenter/Carlos Efrén Reyes Rosado/Franklin Jovani Martinez/Marcos G Perez\n[00:00.13]Sabrina Carpenter：\n[00:00.65]I&apos;m sorry but\n[00:01.45]\n[00:03.25]Don&apos;t wanna talk\n[00:04.66]I need a moment before I go\n[00:08.78]It&apos;s nothing personal\n[00:11.72]I draw the blinds\n[00:13.90]They don&apos;t need to see me cry\n[00:16.57]Cause even if they understand\n[00:19.79]They don&apos;t understand\n[00:23.61]So then when I&apos;m finished\n[00:25.01]I&apos;m all &apos;bout my business\n[00:26.51]And ready to save the world\n[00:29.23]I&apos;m takin&apos; my misery\n[00:30.93]Make it my b***h\n[00:31.86]Can&apos;t be everyone&apos;s favourite girl\n[00:34.68]So take aim and fire away\n[00:37.86]I&apos;ve never been so wide awake\n[00:40.74]No nobody but me can keep me safe\n[00:44.45]And I&apos;m on my way\n[00:46.04]The blood moon is on the rise\n[00:48.82]The fire burning in my eyes\n[00:51.97]No nobody but me can keep me safe\n[00:55.82]And I&apos;m on my way\n[00:57.23]Farruko：\n[01:19.29]Lo siento mucho pero me voy\n[01:25.02]Por que a tu lado me di cuenta que nada so\n[01:30.36]Y me cansé de luchar y de guerrear en van\n[01:33.18]De estar en la línea de fuego y de meter la mano\n[01:36.17]Acepto mis errores también soy humano\n[01:39.17]Y tu no vez que lo Hago por que te amo\n[01:42.25]Pero ya no tengo mas na&apos; que hacer aquí\n[01:46.94]Me voy llego la hora de partir\n[01:49.83]En mi propio camino seguiré lejos de ti\n[01:53.47]Sabrina Carpenter：\n[01:53.70]So take aim and fire away\n[01:56.94]I&apos;ve never been so wide awake\n[01:59.85]No nobody but me can keep me safe\n[02:03.49]And I&apos;m on my way\n[02:05.07]The blood moon is on the rise\n[02:08.04]The fire burning in my eyes\n[02:11.17]No nobody but me can keep me safe\n[02:14.98]And I&apos;m on my way\n[02:26.55]And I&apos;m on my way\n[02:28.68]So I&apos;ve never been\n[02:30.78]Nobody\n[02:31.58]Keep me safe\n[02:32.71]And I&apos;m on my way\n[02:34.31]So I&apos;ve never been\n[02:36.41]Nobody\n[02:37.19]Keep me safe\n[02:38.43]And I&apos;m on my way\n[02:39.92]So I&apos;ve never been\n[02:42.02]Nobody\n[02:42.79]Keep me safe\n[02:44.07]And I&apos;m on my way\n[02:45.60]So I&apos;ve never been\n[02:47.67]Nobody\n[02:48.43]Nobody\n[02:49.12]On my way\n[02:49.97]Sabrina Carpenter：\n[02:50.29]So take aim and fire away\n[02:53.36]I&apos;ve never been so wide awake\n[02:56.35]No nobody but me can keep me safe\n[02:59.93]And I&apos;m on my way\n[03:01.69]The blood moon is on the rise\n[03:04.40]The fire burning in my eyes\n[03:07.43]No nobody but me can keep me safe\n[03:11.36]And I&apos;m on my way"
